{
  "text": "\u2022 Zorowitz et al. tested the effectiveness of four different slings in reducing GHS [CITATION_1] . They found that the only sling that significantly corrected vertical asymmetry was the single-strap hemisling, while total asymmetry was corrected mostly by the Rolyan sling.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "41294682"
